n his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice was born about 1437, in Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom. She married William Blake in 1464, in Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died in 1471, in her hometown, at the age of 35."},"et":{"Abt 1437–1471":"umbes 1437–1471","1438–1471":"1438–1471","1465–1547":"1465–1547","1467–1547":"1467–1547","1470–1502":"1470–1502","1437–1471":"1437–1471","1437":"1437","1547":"1547","ABT 1470":"umbes 1470","1502":"1502","1467":"1467","1465":"1465","1464":"1464","ABT 1467":"umbes 1467","1471":"1471","1470":"1470","Abt 1437":"umbes 1437","1438":"1438","Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Scoreby, Yorkshire, England":"Scoreby, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Caline, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1437–1471":"noin 1437–1471","1438–1471":"1438–1471","1465–1547":"1465–1547","1467–1547":"1467–1547","1470–1502":"1470–1502","1437–1471":"1437–1471","1437":"1437","1547":"1547","ABT 1470":"noin 1470","1502":"1502","1467":"1467","1465":"1465","1464":"1464","ABT 1467":"noin 1467","1471":"1471","1470":"1470","Abt 1437":"noin 1437","1438":"1438","Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Scoreby, Yorkshire, England":"Scoreby, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Caline, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1437–1471":"environ 1437–1471","1438–1471":"1438–1471","1465–1547":"1465–1547","1467–1547":"1467–1547","1470–1502":"1470–15